This paper deals with data management applications and information integration, which are core topics in the database community (cs.DB). The problem of identifying true values from conflicting observations is also a common problem in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper proposes a model that considers conflicts between values, which is a common theme in natural language processing (cs.CL) and machine learning (cs.LG).
